# Branch Safety

Canonical rule lives in `haderach-platform/.cursor/rules/branch-safety-reminder.mdc`. Read that file for the full policy.

**Short version:** Never commit or push directly to main. Always create a feature branch, push with `-u`, open a PR, and merge via `gh pr merge`.
